what:
where:
Abu Dhabi
We are working with one of the major tertiary hospitals in Abu Dhabi to source a Specialist grade Cardiologist ( Non Interventional) . The hospital offers an attractive remuneration package and a challenging clinical, teaching and academic career. The post is at Middle Grade level and the incumbent will be supervised by Consultant Cardiologists.
You must hold the MD (MBCHB, MBBS) degree and have completed Residency training in Internal Medicine and Cardiology and hold a postgraduate qualification in Tier 1,2 or 3 of the HAAD PQR suitable for the Specialist license. Additionally you must have a completed the required experience post qualification for the license category as a Registrar or Specialist in Cardiology preferably at a hospital affiliated with a University or holding intentional accreditation.
Knowledge of Arabic is desirable and English fluency essential.
For further details and applications please send a current CV.
